---
title: Broccoli-Carrot Donburi with a Fried Egg over Scallion Lime Rice with Pickled Radishes & Sesame Seeds
description: Grain bowl–lovers, rejoice! This week, we’re serving up donburi, a Japanese rice bowl dish that can be endlessly customized with different proteins, veggies, and sauces. This version layers steamy scallion-lime rice with saucy broccoli and shredded carrots, plus perfectly fried eggs. Garnish with tangy pickled radishes and nutty sesame seeds, then finish with drizzles of sweet soy glaze and spicy sriracha. Prepare to be totally bowled over!
